cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.NE 

The paper deals with image classification using neural networks, which is a core topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also proposes a new learning method that combines learning to learn and learning by analogy, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also involves natural language processing (cs.CL) as it discusses the use of analogies in learning. Finally, the paper proposes a new model for classification, which involves regression (cs.NE).
